  He watched as the battle continued. What was this beam the bot used. It was 
quite large yet some how the bot he was attacking dodged it. The sensors from 
the masquito could not scan it do it its enourmonsy. He had to see it for 
himself. His eyes sensors lifted. He powered up and lifted off. His dragon 
wings spread wide. He saw them come inot view. Hed stop  in a minute about 
500 feeet from where they where battleing. The two should not reconize him. 
And Prime had not seen his new body yet. So he sat back and enjoyed the show.
